{"tid":832682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地女西九站落車即吐痰 一腳往返兩地成打卡熱點","createTime":"2018-09-23T03:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:36:59.000Z","uid":29675,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"439007196fcafdc1df7714fc4ffdecdbd2da81cf","tid":832682,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:15:11.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵香港段今日通車，《蘋果》記者今晨6時許就抵達廣州南站，直擊第一班車的情況，不僅看到了中港兩地車站規矩的大不同，還目擊到乘客在月台吐痰的嚇人情景，見證兩地文化的差異！<br />\n廣州南站離市區甚遠，記者實測從越秀區鬧市，乘搭地鐵到廣州南站，需近30分鐘地鐵車程；按百度地圖顯示，從天河區、海珠區等市中心乘搭地鐵到廣州南站，行程均為約30分鐘。而在廣州南站月台上，記者發現，一名男子正在吸煙。原來，內地車站的規例與香港大不同，西九龍站內是禁止吸煙的，但廣州南站和深圳北站均無此規定。<br />\n記者登車後，6時48分，列車開出，7時43分準時抵港。不過，甫落車，記者就看到嚇人一幕，有女乘客落車踏上月台後，即吐出一口濃痰！<br />\n廣州南下第一班高鐵抵達西九龍站，旅客還是非常興奮，內地口岸區與香港口岸區的分界線，成為了打卡熱點，不少乘客跨過地上的黃黑色分界線，拍下「一腳往返兩地」的照片留念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537663342_3bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537663342_3bda.jpg&h=b039fa60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名女乘客甫抵西九龍站，即在月台吐痰（左圖）。右圖為「一腳往返兩地」打卡熱點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537663342_1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537663342_1200.jpg&h=e77326cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少人在內地口岸區與香港口岸區的分界線上，拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537663342_256e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537663342_256e.jpg&h=f291df9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男子在廣州南站月台上吸煙。"},{"pid":"036068c3a9070e9a90e14c14802ce38e66276027","tid":832682,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"24c35cdb4bd6454dfef6fc01e7cc8aff2406431f","tid":832682,"uid":80560,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"商女不知亡國恨 隔江猶唱後庭花<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c693bd8964d7250feebb1a184665ad89971d221d","tid":832682,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"霸個地盤先"},{"pid":"7c9f7bedda9ef4c426fb8d6b09c2fe7cc253bb61","tid":832682,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c541388319af808cf15426befa4c462c92831628","tid":832682,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76257d7740df631462e09d427fe1a09ca01b2e5","tid":832682,"uid":67771,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"所有邊境都係一腳往返兩地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d025b5285adee0e9e45d046dc8f1b27aa9dfb8d3","tid":832682,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"吐痰咪由鳩佢囉， 仲喺大陸嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283ebb6d13eb9ef26ef0f162836ce55cf22d5145","tid":832682,"uid":44083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"黃狗射尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428ab1ac94980c428159c63dc48b9c5887e77d7d","tid":832682,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:26:49.000Z","msg":"點解要落車先吐痰？車上唔吐得咩？"},{"pid":"b9f48dd4a509fa99c7e5334cee21cf4d65d523a7","tid":832682,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:27:00.000Z","msg":"未必係痰 岩岩係車比人口爆"},{"pid":"b66cde422e78c041f47db02753